ps://www.webcitation.org/6PCNnwys0?url=http://marvel.com/news/movies/2011/8/2/16398/marvel_one-shots_expanding_the_cinematic_universe |archivedate=April 29, 2014 |url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"CBRBigger\">{{cite web|url=http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&id=47791 |title=Marvel Studios' Short Films Get Bigger With \"Agent Carter\" |last=Ching |first=Albert |publisher=[[Comic Book Resources]] |date=September 9, 2013 |accessdate=November 27, 2014 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6UOJRULVh?url=http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&id=47791 |archivedate=November 27, 2014 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Collider\">{{cite web|url=https://collider.com/agent-carter-louis-desposito-brad-winderbaum-interview/ |title=Director Louis D\u2019Esposito and Executive Producer Brad Winderbaum Talk Marvel One-Shot: Agent Carter, Future Shorts, More Peggy Carter Stories, and More |last=Radish |first=Christina |publisher=[[Collider (website)|Collider]] |accessdate=November 27, 2014 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6UOJa0Cos?url=http://collider.com/agent-carter-louis-desposito-brad-winderbaum-interview/ |archivedate=November 27, 2014 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Nerdist\">{{cite web |url=http://www.nerdist.com/2013/09/marvels-louis-desposito-talks-agent-carter/ |title=Marvel's Louis D\u2019Esposito Talks Agent Carter |last=Anderson |first=Kyle |publisher=Nerdist |date=September 24, 2014 |accessdate=November 27, 2014 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6UOJhmUun?url=http://www.nerdist.com/2013/09/marvels-louis-desposito-talks-agent-carter/ |archivedate=November 27, 2014 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Perception\">{{cite web|url=http://perceptionnyc.com/content/agent-carter-case-study |title=Agent Carter Case Study |publisher=Perception |accessdate=November 27, 2014 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6UOJqUs46?url=http://perceptionnyc.com/content/agent-carter-case-study |archivedate=November 27, 2014 |url-st