 Alliance]] |date=March 28, 2014 |accessdate=July 8, 2014 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Qv5j8xl6?url=http://comicsalliance.com/marvel-gay-punchlines-mandarin-short-one-shot-justin-hammer-thor-dark-world-lgbt-joke/ |archivedate=July 8, 2014 |url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"AHTKMovieweb\">{{cite web|url=http://www.movieweb.com/news/marvel-previews-marvel-one-shot-all-hail-the-king |title=Marvel Previews 'Marvel One-Shot: All Hail the King' |last=Gallagher |first=Brian |publisher=[[MovieWeb]] |date=February 25, 2014 |accessdate=April 19, 2014 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6OwV4nuEz?url=http://www.movieweb.com/news/marvel-previews-marvel-one-shot-all-hail-the-king |archivedate=April 19, 2014 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"PearceEmpire\">{{cite web|url=https://www.empireonline.com/interviews/interview.asp?IID=1848 |title=Drew Pearce on Making Marvel One-Shot All Hail The King |last=Plumb |first=Ali |work=[[Empire (film magazine)|Empire]] |date=February 24, 2014 |accessdate=February 25, 2014 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6NdvHxegQ?url=http://www.empireonline.com/interviews/interview.asp?IID=1848 |archivedate=February 25, 2014 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"PearceSR\">{{cite web|url=https://screenrant.com/iron-man-4-mandarin-runaways-marvel-interview/ |title=Drew Pearce Talks 'All Hail The King', Runaways, The Real Mandarin & Marvel Future |last=Keyes |first=Rob |publisher=ScreenRant |date=February 27, 2014 |accessdate=October 26, 2015 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140227225329/http://screenrant.com/iron-man-4-mandarin-runaways-marvel-interview/ |archivedate=February 27, 2014 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<!-- Collection -->\n\n<ref name=\"PhaseTwoBoxset\">{{cite web|url=https://collider.com/mcu-phase-2-box-set-image-bonus-features/ |title='Marvel Cinematic Universe: Phase Two Collection' Unveiled; Contains First Look at Phase 3 |last=Goldberg |first=Matt |publisher=[[Collider (website)|Collider]] |date=October 23, 2015 |accessdate=October 23, 2015 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6cV3n4hc2?url=http://collider.com/mcu-phase-2-box-set-image-bonus-features/ |archivedate=October 23, 2015 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<!-- Reception -->\n\n<ref name=\"ComingSoonConsultant\">{{cite web|last=Chitwood |first=Scott |date=August 29, 2011 |title=Thor (Limited 3D Edition) (Blu-ray) |url=https://www.comingsoon.net/news/dvdreviewsnews.php?id=81975 |publisher=[[ComingSoon.net]] |accessdate=January 14, 2014 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Mce7ACMh?url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/dvdreviewsnews.php?id=81975 |archivedate=January 14, 2014 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"IGNHammer\">{{cite web|last=Shaffer |first=R.L. |date=August 29, 2011 |title=Thor (Limited 3D Edition) (Blu-ray) |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2011/10/25/captain-america-the-first-avenger-blu-ray-review |publisher=[[IGN]] |accessdate=January 14, 2014 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Mceq6yTZ?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2011/10/25/captain-america-the-first-avenger-blu-ray-review |archivedate=January 14, 2014 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"CinemaBlendHammer\">{{cite web|last=Scheer |first=Zachary |date=August 29, 2011 |title=Captain America: The First Avenger [Blu-Ray] |url=https://www.cinemablend.com/dvds/Captain-America-The-First-Avenger-Blu-Ray-5554.html |publisher=Cinema Blend |accessdate=January 14, 2014 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Mcf050MU?url=http://www.cinemablend.com/dvds/Captain-America-The-First-Avenger-Blu-Ray-5554.html |archivedate=January 14, 2014 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"CraveOnlineItem47\">{{cite web |last=Dellamorte |first=Andre |date=July 14, 2012 |title=Comic-Con 2012 Review: Marvel One-Shots: Item 47 |url=http://www.craveonline.com/film/reviews/192191-comic-con-2012-review-marvel-one-shots-item-47 |publisher=[[CraveOnline]] |accessdate=January 14, 2014 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Mcgs9AKv?url=http://www.craveonline.com/film/reviews/192191-comic-con-2012-review-marvel-one-shots-item-47 |archivedate=January 14, 2014 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ColliderItem47\">{{cite web|last=Dellamorte |first=Andre |date=September 20, 2012 |title=THE AVENGERS Blu-ray Review |url=https://collider.com/the-avengers-blu-ray-review/ |publisher=Collider |accessdate=January 14, 2014 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Mcgbhho4?url=http://collider.com/the-avengers-blu-ray-review/ |archivedate=January 14, 2014 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"SHHItem47\">{{cite web|last=Terry |first=Spencer |date=September 20, 2012 |title=Marvel's The Avengers Blu-ray Review |url=http://www.superherohype.com/features/articles/172797-review-the-avengers-blu-ray |publisher=Superhero Hype! |accessdate=January 14, 2014 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6McgjWd0A?url=http://www.superherohype.com/features/articles/172797-review-the-avengers-blu-ray |archivedate=January 14, 2014 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"CraveOnlineAgentCarter\">{{cite web |last=Hunsaker |first=Andy |date=July 20, 2013 |title=Comic-Con 2013: Marvel's 'Agent Carter': Happy Ending or a New Beginning? |url=http://www.craveonline.com/comics/reviews/538805-marvels-agent-carter-one-shot-a-happy-ending-and-a-new-beginning#/slide/1 |publisher=[[CraveOnline]] |accessdate=January 14, 2014 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6MckJDVF3?url=http://www.craveonline.com/comics/reviews/538805-marvels-agent-carter-one-shot-a-happy-ending-and-a-new-beginning#/slide/1 |archivedate=January 14, 2014 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"IGNAgentCarter\">{{cite web|last=Collura |first=Scott |date=July 19, 2013 |title=Comic-Con: We Have Seen Agent Carter, the New Marvel One-Shot \u2013 and It Rules |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2013/07/20/comic-con-we-have-seen-agent-carter-the-new-marvel-one-shot-and-it-rules |publisher=[[IGN]] |accessdate=January 14, 2014 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6MckWZvcu?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/07/20/comic-con-we-have-seen-agent-carter-the-new-marvel-one-shot-and-it-rules |archivedate=January 14, 2014 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"IGNAHTK\">{{cite web|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2014/02/25/marvel-one-shot-all-hail-the-king-review |title='You'll... never...' and so on. |last=Wheatley |first=Cliff |publisher=[[IGN]] |date=February 24, 2014 |accessdate=February 25, 2014 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6NdutFEad?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/02/25/marvel-one-shot-all-hail-the-king-review |archivedate=February 25, 2014 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<!-- Potential projects -->\n\n<ref name=\"Prologue\">{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/chinese-actors-cut-iron-man-519687 |title=Chinese Actors Cut From 'Iron Man 3' to Be Featured in Short Film |last=Tsui |first=Clarence |work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=May 8, 2013 |accessdate=January 7, 2017 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6nLnQ0xMV?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/chinese-actors-cut-iron-man-519687 |archivedate=January 8, 2017 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"PearceTotalFilm\">{{cite web|url=http://www.totalfilm.com/features/all-hail-the-king-drew-pearce-interview |title=All Hail The King: Drew Pearce Interview |last=Risley |first=Matt |work=[[Total Film]] |date=February 6, 2014 |accessdate=February 6, 2014 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Qv5Uoczv?url=http://www.totalfilm.com/features/all-hail-the-king-drew-pearce-interview |archivedate=July 8, 2014 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"FeigeMay2015\">{{cite web|url=http://www.comicbookresources.com/article/feige-talks-contract-death-and-if-marvels-movies-will-take-a-dark-turn |title=Feige Talks Contract, Death And If Marvel's Movies Will Take A 'Dark Turn' |last=White |first=Brett |publisher=[[Comic Book Resources]] |date=May 7, 2015 |accessdate=May 7, 2015 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6YMQf4Gxa?url=http://www.comicbookresources.com/article/feige-